name: Anaerobic Endurance #1
description:
Anaerobic Endurance involves high cadence and big power, and the ability to resist fatigue. After completing a good warm-up, the principal sets consist of 4 x 60 seconds at 121%FTP, with 3min recovery. 



Throughout each 60sec interval, observe your cadence and heart rate. Is your cadence dropping with fatigue and your heart rate rising?
